{"tid":2387637,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★PS5群組ready！PS5 日本供不應求　秋葉原亂象橫生！人群中不少是中國人！","createTime":"2021-01-30T13:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T04:29:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"55d397bb2c141a1849937248f2abf568f7764bef","tid":2387637,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Es8jOL5U4AEYOEL-1280x854.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2FEs8jOL5U4AEYOEL-1280x854.jpeg&h=729df6d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從去年 Sony 推出 PS5 以來，缺貨問題一直都存在，不只在香港，在「主場」日本亦一直供不應求。最近在秋葉原就有電器店開放現貨發售，但就引起搶購亂象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1355332446862991364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1355332446862991364&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=27fead6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1355332446862991364&h=824647b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1355332446862991364</a><br />\n<br />\n秋葉原的 Yodobashi 今日有現貨 PS5 發售，不過開售之後人潮就迫滿派籌的櫃檯，令派籌無法繼續進行，連櫃檯也有損毀，甚至需要出動警察維持秩序。結果 Yodobashi 決定取消今日的 PS5 現貨發售活動，需要再次考慮發售方式。有網民指在<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>人群中有不少是中國人</strong></span>和專業炒家，抱怨他們令一般人無法購買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/30/ps5-japan-chaos/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F30%2Fps5-japan-chaos%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=7534f7a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/30/ps5-japan-chaos/game-channel/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，目前東京仍然在緊急狀態之下，政府強烈勸喻民衆沒有必要應該留在家中，不過數據顯示當日在秋葉原站進出的人數比緊急狀態公佈當日（1 月 8 日）增加了 29.8%。有意見認為電器店應該維持以往的網上抽籤發售模式，而非現貨排隊發售，避免混亂以及擁擠的情況。"},{"pid":"716fa0a73485be494add167ca4f0cdd576c53b98","tid":2387637,"uid":103262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:00:50.000Z","msg":"老貓u 啲同鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55e72d8c9c64c9644e99bf12e57d5d940dcd040","tid":2387637,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTcUjoh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTcUjoh.jpg&h=87b8308b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eeac5a28283fdb6c736911dc56c2d7612fc62b15","tid":2387637,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"716fa0a73485be494add167ca4f0cdd576c53b98","tid":2387637,"uid":103262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:00:50.000Z","msg":"老貓u 啲同鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALK2ndf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALK2ndf.gif&h=2e3fa733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"879f2fd94d0fd01be41e3d21eb23de435335073a","tid":2387637,"uid":47462,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXAyfA6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXAyfA6.gif&h=49142a5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1615c1c0ca156982425d030ca165679f517e96fc","tid":2387637,"uid":179810,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T13:33:57.000Z","msg":"日本ps5 唔係無人問津咩？"},{"pid":"8d9ad7184c7076562c0f74fc69c6a847418870cd","tid":2387637,"uid":75479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1615c1c0ca156982425d030ca165679f517e96fc","tid":2387637,"uid":179